            <section class="project-content">
                <h2>Project Overview</h2>
                <p>A comprehensive suite of automation tools designed for streamlining industrial processes, including data collection, analysis, and reporting. Built using Python and industry-standard automation frameworks to improve efficiency and reduce manual workload.</p>

                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Automated data collection from multiple sources</li>
                    <li>Real-time process monitoring and alerts</li>
                    <li>Customizable reporting templates</li>
                    <li>Integration with industrial control systems</li>
                    <li>Error handling and logging system</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Technical Details</h2>
                <h3>Core Technologies</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Python for core automation logic</li>
                    <li>Pandas for data processing</li>
                    <li>PyAutoGUI for UI automation</li>
                    <li>Schedule for task scheduling</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Integration Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>REST API endpoints for data exchange</li>
                    <li>Database connectivity (SQL, MongoDB)</li>
                    <li>Industrial protocol support (Modbus, OPC-UA)</li>
                    <li>Email and notification systems</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Development Process</h2>
                <p>The development followed an agile methodology:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Process analysis and requirements gathering</li>
                    <li>Tool architecture design</li>
                    <li>Core functionality implementation</li>
                    <li>Integration with existing systems</li>
                    <li>Testing and deployment</li>
                    <li>User training and documentation</li>
                </ol>

                <h2>Results and Impact</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Reduced manual data entry by 90%</li>
                    <li>Improved data accuracy to 99.9%</li>
                    <li>Saved approximately 20 hours per week in manual tasks</li>
                    <li>Standardized reporting across departments</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Key Achievements</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Successfully automated Windows Server Update Service (WSUS) deployment for 1200 virtual machines</li>
                    <li>Reduced administrative overhead by an estimated 4500 hours per year</li>
                    <li>Implemented robust error handling and recovery mechanisms</li>
                    <li>Created comprehensive documentation and training materials</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>AI/ML integration for predictive maintenance</li>
                    <li>Extended industrial protocol support</li>
                    <li>Enhanced visualization capabilities</li>
                    <li>Mobile app integration</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
